The,eBay,Merchandising,API,retrieves,relevant,information,about,products,or,item,listings,on,eBay,to,help,users,sell,more,merchandise,to,eBay,buyers,This,API,can,be,used,to,create,applications,that,provide,suggested,products,or,item,listings,based,on,buyers,searching,or,selection,activity,Sellers,can,also,use,this,API,to,augment,their,own,listings,with,cross,promotions,for,their,users